OL,3,CRail regulator does U-turn on plans to
OL,4,Crun early morning 'ghost train' to
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FFrom December 15, the 7am service -
OL,8,Fnicknamed the "ghost train" - would
OL,9,Fhave been forced to run with only
OL,10,Fstaff on board so that it could be
OL,11,Feasily moved or delayed to alleviate
OL,12,Fpressure on rail services.
OL,14,FBut on Monday, the rail regulator
OL,15,Freversed its decision.
