OL,3,CRail regulator does U-turn on plans to
OL,4,Crun early morning 'ghost train' to
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA spokesperson for ORR told ITV News:
OL,8,F"We have taken account of all the
OL,9,Fevidence and feedback, and we have
OL,10,Fgiven Network Rail and Avanti the go-
OL,11,Fahead to arrange for the 7am service
OL,12,Fto continue running with passengers."
OL,14,FThe regulator added: "Although it
OL,15,Fcould have a negative impact on
OL,16,Freliability and punctuality of
OL,17,Fservices on the West Coast Main Line,
OL,18,Fwe understand the importance of this
OL,19,Fservice and we'll support its
OL,20,Fcontinued operation.
