OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,F"We expect train operators and Network
OL,8,FRail to look at how to best mitigate
OL,9,Fthe performance impacts."
OL,11,FThe statement comes after public
OL,12,Foutcry over the move.
OL,14,FAvanti was originally granted rights
OL,15,Fto run the service from May to
OL,16,FDecember 2025. However, this timetable
OL,17,Fwill end on December 15, and new
OL,18,Fservices by the electric train
OL,19,Foperator Lumo will begin, adding to
OL,20,Fthe number of trains on the West Coast
OL,21,FMain Line.
