OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FThis meant that if Avanti's 7am
OL,8,Fservice continued, it would have to
OL,9,Fuse a "firebreak path," which is
OL,10,Fessentially a free slot in the
OL,11,Ftimetable to help operators reduce
OL,12,Fknock-on delays to their services
OL,13,Fafter they are disrupted.
OL,15,FThe ORR said Avanti could run trains
OL,16,Fat 7am from Manchester to London, with
OL,17,Fstaff but no passengers, as these
OL,18,F"firebreak" services are easier to
OL,19,Fmove or delay.
