OL,7,FA spokesperson for Avanti told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "We are delighted that the
OL,9,FOffice of Rail and Road has given us
OL,10,Fpermission to reinstate the 07:00
OL,11,FManchester to Euston weekday service
OL,12,Fin our December timetable.
OL,14,F"The original decision would have had
OL,15,Fa detrimental impact on customers who
OL,16,Fuse this train, and this development
OL,17,Fis a welcome boost for those who want
OL,18,Fto take advantage of a sub two-hour
OL,19,Fservice between two of the UK's major
OL,20,Fcities."
